見慣れたり 聞いたりの 眺め
Scenes I've seen and heard so often

12
00:08:23,688 --> 00:08:26,988
理屈を超える 変化を求めていた
I was seeking a change that defies logic

13
00:08:27,388 --> 00:08:30,788
窮屈で 退屈な 日々の中
In the middle of cramped and boring days

14
00:08:31,088 --> 00:08:34,488
